name: milkingtable
description:
First attempt at creating a model to replicate "milking table" or "table glory hole" style images. Trained on still images, gifs, and still from 720p+ videos.

Use keyword "milkingtable" to trigger. Other keywords to get some variations include "oral," "licking," and "handjob." Seems to work best between 0.7 and 0.9 strength and above, but you can also weight each keyword to finetune the image.

It does not always get it right. Almost always, you end up with a woman under a table. It will frequently misplace the penis or have it floating in the frame. Some of these blemishes can be remedied via inpainting after the image is generated
